[Student "S"]
{This is a companion hand to Deal 16.

EAST shows four \Ss following WEST's Stayman bid.

So WEST ignores her five \Hs, having already found 
an 8-card Major suit fit. With the fit her hand now revalues to 11 points so she bids 4\S.}

